      "content": "Look, the situation in the border region is getting a bit noisy in the press. The Ambassador is asking for a preliminary assessment before the summit. We need to be careful here—we don't want to trigger any premature policy shifts or unnecessary panic in the markets if these reports turn out to be nothing. Are there any actually credible indicators of a military escalation on the horizon, or is this just more geopolitical chatter and rumors?",
